{"tid":1572763,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【回帶檢討】自私既香港人唔配有民主 革命係用血用汗 踩住鮮血去爭取番嚟","createTime":"2019-09-15T18:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T04:04:55.000Z","uid":97155,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"32a2e2cfe53a746483ace527f4f847920e287c1c","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先今日私了係一大進步 勇武前線值得大家欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我地要檢討下呢排點解前線陣地戰好似愈打愈弱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然其中一個好直接既原因係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府縱容黑警濫捕濫暴</span></span>搞到人心惶惶 你睇今日就算連遊行 只要冇不反就少左咁多人敢行出嚟就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"color: orange;\">但係喺中線見到好大既問題係中後線既心態問題 人人一見到有咩風吹草動 十幾個黑警防暴舉下旗出嚟吠下就</span>[/size=4<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">]散水</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">搞到往往前線冇曬支援 自己係前面搵命搏 擰轉身就散得七七八八</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初叫中後線企散啲個原意係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有起事上嚟有得比前線退後</span> </span> 而更重要係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前線後退之後有一大埋同路人支援</span></span> 令到黑警冇咁大信心衝過嚟咬人 咁先可以減低前線手足被捕同受傷既機會啊!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家係現場成日中線後線走得仲快過前線 搞到成日防線都未SET好就已經比加有機會衝出嚟咬人 中後線冇人前線都只可以比狗追住打 你話咁樣我地仲點保護前線手足啊??<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 我明大家日日睇住手足比狗打 拉左去新屋嶺就用私刑 喺街盲有藍絲廢老支那人打人砍人 黨鐵醫管局都同流合污 真係會好驚 因為我都好驚好淆底!!</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係前線咁驚都照勇武 照為左大家企出嚟 押上前途 擋刀擋子彈</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問心你要背住佢地走你良心過唔過意得去啊?? 香港人可唔可以唔好再咁自私 再依賴其他人為自己既未來賣命啊?? 勇武對住槍炮都係得個勇字嫁咋</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人數先係我地最大既武器同盾牌啊!!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">而家唔係叫你衝上去同前線一齊勇武抗爭 大家只要唔會一下就散曬 睇清形勢先跑 走完冇事番轉頭繼續喺安全距離支持前線就幫到好多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 我地一齊重溫下當年雨革眼鏡哥哥條片 香港人好叻 五年後今日學識不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰 繼續努力行多一步 大家為香港付出多小小好唔好?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1035263196500611/?v=1035263196500611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsocrec%2Fvideos%2F1035263196500611%2F%3Fv%3D1035263196500611&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=08fa6441\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1035263196500611/?v=1035263196500611</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 中線 自問懦弱唔敢上最前 但永遠唔會掉低前線手足"},{"pid":"9b70573fbbff1953b8f408338eaffc6e876ebcea","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:22:48.000Z","msg":"自推 希望更多中後線睇到"},{"pid":"9634761333416ce5b60f593501a561e9caedb2ad","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:23:19.000Z","msg":"自推 中後線需要更多抗爭教育"},{"pid":"704fed7dc66b556a356ff83a2723699ad896ff42","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"自推 唔可以再比前線手足做condom"},{"pid":"85ddc6709055c3952a2ab63aeab6556061391229","tid":1572763,"uid":293667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:25:15.000Z","msg":"岳義士一救三 我地要為佢行落去<br />\n咁先可以真正幫到佢"},{"pid":"429cd95747260f1dd04cab5824655b3fad92040f","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:25:35.000Z","msg":"成日話齊上齊落 但係成日有落冇上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8364e42e8f7d7beab9cea8c7ebb59597dcbd7ed9","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:27:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a97c110d6181f047bb193911b501a6527db29854","tid":1572763,"uid":306180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一時又屌中線唔識走/走得慢<br />\n一時又屌中線散水"},{"pid":"1e1c1c3d1903efb17980b7bb58cfc06035394ca6","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:30:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人發夢有同感? 定連登得番mon po 狗?"},{"pid":"5fd140b02ceae17a509adbc4aa42631132c5f30b","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a97c110d6181f047bb193911b501a6527db29854","tid":1572763,"uid":306180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一時又屌中線唔識走/走得慢<br />\n一時又屌中線散水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:32:54.000Z","msg":"事實係呢排成日一轉身中線就散曬 明明煙又未放 啲狗有時連人都未齊<br />\n唔係叫唔好