:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb0ede897dd1e86238cd8f1748c152c7d7768b1d","tid":1572763,"uid":312696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T19:19:34.000Z","msg":"大約5點去到金鐘都未想走, 但有幾次就有散水人士大叫, 之後後面有人大堆人又跑幾步咁....  搞到我有次都跟住要跑, 唔係驚黑警, 係驚班被盲毛人踩人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"推 exact7ly <br />\n琴日發夢喺灣仔狗屋個咩事都未有前線仲佈緊防 就有人話金鐘政總放左煙係咁叫人走 搞到防線都未set好已經開始散 而嗰時係得十幾隻狗係橋上面 淨係舉咗橙旗豬咀都冇戴 啲人走都咁上下又冇回頭啲狗就推"},{"pid":"f03ae1e4df7b051bb8fd9e2334a8dabc5bcade39","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbe52a0f52d3a74ea523fb702249f1efabab9a1d","tid":1572763,"uid":200992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T20:03:54.000Z","msg":"發夢夢見勇武手足係現場已經多次因為咁屌曬鬼 中後排比多啲吉士一齊抗爭好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:11:45.000Z","msg":"係 一係就未有事已經散 一係就散到次次得番前線喺到比狗咬 好多時個勢根本唔差 香港人變左驚弓之鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dd10742dccf8323adf3770545bd41464f7d7ad","tid":1572763,"uid":89848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32a2e2cfe53a746483ace527f4f847920e287c1c","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先今日私了係一大進步 勇武前線值得大家欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我地要檢討下呢排點解前線陣地戰好似愈打愈弱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然其中一個好直接既原因係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府縱容黑警濫捕濫暴</span></span>搞到人心惶惶 你睇今日就算連遊行 只要冇不反就少左咁多人敢行出嚟就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"color: orange;\">但係喺中線見到好大既問題係中後線既心態問題 人人一見到有咩風吹草動 十幾個黑警防暴舉下旗出嚟吠下就</span>[/size=4<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">]散水</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">搞到往往前線冇曬支援 自己係前面搵命搏 擰轉身就散得七七八八</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初叫中後線企散啲個原意係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有起事上嚟有得比前線退後</span> </span> 而更重要係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前線後退之後有一大埋同路人支援</span></span> 令到黑警冇咁大信心衝過嚟咬人 咁先可以減低前線手足被捕同受傷既機會啊!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家係現場成日中線後線走得仲快過前線 搞到成日防線都未SET好就已經比加有機會衝出嚟咬人 中後線冇人前線都只可以比狗追住打 你話咁樣我地仲點保護前線手足啊??<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 我明大家日日睇住手足比狗打 拉左去新屋嶺就用私刑 喺街盲有藍絲廢老支那人打人砍人 黨鐵醫管局都同流合污 真係會好驚 因為我都好驚好淆底!!</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係前線咁驚都照勇武 照為左大家企出嚟 押上前途 擋刀擋子彈</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問心你要背住佢地走你良心過唔過意得去啊?? 香港人可唔可以唔好再咁自私 再依賴其他人為自己既未來賣命啊?? 勇武對住槍炮都係得個勇字嫁咋</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人數先係我地最大既武器同盾牌啊!!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">而家唔係叫你衝上去同前線一齊勇武抗爭 大家只要唔會一下就散曬 睇清形勢先跑 走完冇事番轉頭繼續喺安全距離支持前線就幫到好多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 我地一齊重溫下當年雨革眼鏡哥哥條片 香港人好叻 五年後今日學識不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰 繼續努力行多一步 大家為香港付出多小小好唔好?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1035263196500611/?v=1035263196500611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsocrec%2Fvideos%2F1035263196500611%2F%3Fv%3D1035263196500611&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=08fa6441\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1035263196500611/?v=1035263196500611</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 中線 自問懦弱唔敢上最前 但永遠唔會掉低前線手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"陣地戰無優勢，而且好易有太多損耗，burn and run好D"},{"pid":"76b2317bc89b27f7f494b65af3137e12a9696a55","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf8a4fd591522bf96a12c93937cc4e13a9f4141","tid":1572763,"uid":200992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:22:43.000Z","msg":"推 呢啲係無記者會報導嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不完美 要改善啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"真心想檢討下我哋呢排點解輸𡁵"},{"pid":"51ce62817175a55b784080009dd38d8116732d4d","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0dd10742dccf8323adf3770545bd41464f7d7ad","tid":1572763,"uid":89848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32a2e2cfe53a746483ace527f4f847920e287c1c","tid":1572763,"uid":97155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:21:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先今日私了係一大進步 勇武前線值得大家欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我地要檢討下呢排點解前線陣地戰好似愈打愈弱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然其中一個好直接既原因係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府縱容黑警濫捕濫暴</span></span>搞到人心惶惶 你睇今日就算連遊行 只要冇不反就少左咁多人敢行出嚟就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"colo